  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A researcher wakes up alone, trapped in a dark building, drawn into the heart of a sinister experiment.<br><br><strong>Unstoppable: Breakout</strong> is an exhilarating action game based on a souls-like system. Strategic thinking and resource management are essential, and as night deepens, you'll face increasingly menacing enemies. <br><br>This game delivers relentless tension through its rich art style and gripping soundtrack, characterized by the unsettling atmosphere revealed during exploration. <br><br>Will you uncover the dark secrets? <br><br>The fight for survival in this mysterious space is finally beginning. <br>Step into the darkness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967180/extras/9a3a0a70f00c9077abfa1c61fd7f114d.poster.avif?t=1733133645\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967180/extras/9a3a0a70f00c9077abfa1c61fd7f114d.webm?t=1733133645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967180/extras/f964ca7fa0f12f41cf052ae26691dc08.poster.avif?t=1733133645\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967180/extras/f964ca7fa0f12f41cf052ae26691dc08.webm?t=1733133645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2967180/extras/8e9c942876889fb542bc27340c44a63d.poster.avif?t=1733133645\" width=60